      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2017 Shelby GT350, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the 5.2L 'Voodoo' V8 with its signature flat-plane crankshaft, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,250 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Tremec TR-3160 six-speed manual transmission and a 3.73 Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with the MagneRide Damping System, providing millisecond-level adjustments to damping rates for optimized contact patch consistency. Braking is handled by Brembo six-piston front calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing zero heat checking. This vehicle has been maintained in a climate-controlled environment; the factory finish remains flawless, and the undercarriage retains its assembly-line cleanliness with no signs of oxidation or track abuse.",
